data.title: Manufacturer of the world’s best false eyelashes
data.meta_description: Eyelashesworld.com by PT Bintang Mas Triyasa is an Indonesian leading manufacturer for false eyelashes. We specialize in designing, manufacturing and distributing false eyelashes to customers world-wide. We offer customer driven Private Label/OEM/ODM.
data.text:
With years of experience in false eyelashes business, we can provide you with high quality false eyelashes products. Located in the rural town of Purbalingga, Jawa Tengah, Indonesia, we specialize in designing, manufacturing and distributing false eyelashes to customers world-wide. We have exported our products to many countries in America, Europe, Middle East and Asia.

We can assure our customers that with our experience and knowledge of the false eyelashes market, no one can beat the service and quality of products we supply. Understanding our industry inspires us to offer a higher level of service including fast, affordable, and reliable delivery.

Come on in and see for yourself all the false eyelashes that Indonesia has to offer. You’ll be truly amazed!
